      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not entirely sure exporting this is right since nothing is actually enforcing it. It\u0027s very easy not to respect this max, which makes this a suggestion exported as a const. Not for this CL, but I wonder if we should move step compression and decompression to Save/Load...\n\nhttps://godoc.org/go.chromium.org/luci/gae/service/datastore#PropertyLoadSaver\n\nhttps://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/a96275fbc1522709531d1d140a019d8b9fb556bb/buildbucket/appengine/model/build.go#110",
      "revId": "28b34bdb539108b18add01efea727ffdb2ba0e0c",
